Deploying
--------------
terraform init : intiialize terraform where your code is stored. 
terraform plan : query the api and compare what is currently deployed with what should deploy with terraform code.
terrafrom apply --auto-approve : to apply and run your terraform code .
terrafrom apply -target <resource name>


Destroying resources
-------------------
terraform destry : to delete all deployment terraform done.
terrafrom destroy -target <resource name>


Printing
-----------
terraform state list : list all deployed resources
terraform state list <resource name>
terrafrm state show <resourcename> : show resource details
terraform output : prints all teraform aoutput values
egs:
output "name" {

value = <resourcename.property>
}




